            <author xml:lang="fr" source="#bib552-1">Pallade</author>
            <note xml:lang="syr" type="incipit" source="#bib552-1">
               <quote>ܕܝܪܝܐ ܚܕ ܐܟܣܢܝܐ ܘܢܟܦܐ ܒܕܘܒܪ̈ܘܗܝ: ܕܐܝܬܘܗܝ ܗܘ̣ܐ ܡܢ ܐܢܛܘܟܝܐ ܡܕܝܢܬܐ...</quote>
            </note>
            <note xml:lang="fr" type="incipit" source="#bib552-1">
               <quote>Un moine étranger et à la vie pure, qui provenait de la ville d’Antioche…</quote>
            </note>
            <note xml:lang="syr" type="explicit" source="#bib552-1">
               <quote>ܘܐܦ ܠܟܘܢ ܢܫܬܟܢ ܚܘܣܝܐ. ܐܡܝܢ.</quote>
            </note>
            <note xml:lang="fr" type="explicit" source="#bib552-1">
               <quote>Et qu’à vous aussi soit accordée l’absolution. Amen.</quote>
            </note>
            <note type="editions">
               <bibl source="#bib552-1">
                  <author>Bedjan, P.</author>
                  <title>AMS 7</title>
